{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Cry of Athena is sandbox battle simulator built for VR and PC where you create epic physics based battles, intervene as a giant god with massive god hands, or join in the battle yourself on the battlegrounds!<strong>\u00a0</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1174770/extras/Steam_DIvider@2x.png?t=1728233343\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1174770/extras/grapeshot.gif?t=1728233343\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>In Cry of Athena..</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Create your own fully physics based battles with a variety of AI types including the minotaur, siege weapons, and modern day soldiers!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fight on the battlefield as a mortal, a god, or simply spectate the battle - the choice is yours!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Be a giant god with huge fists that can crush enemies and fling them mercilessly into the skies!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Destroy buildings and deform the voxel based terrain, or build your own levels by shaping the land!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Command your army down to the individual level to follow, charge, or let them act on their own accord!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose from a large arsenal of weapons and combat mechanics - fight with sword or bow, guns or cannons, or as a massive all-mighty god.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play in both VR OR non-VR PC!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Local coop in the form of a VR player and a mouse and keyboard player!  </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1174770/extras/Steam_